<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:TariqRamadan.jpg" class="image" title="TariqRamadan.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/c8/TariqRamadan.jpg" width="170" height="255" border="0" /></a><br />
