<li><i>Radical Reform: Islamic Ethics and Liberation, 2009. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780195331714" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-19-533171-4</a></i></li>
<li><i>In the Footsteps of the Prophet: Lessons from the Life of Muhammad</i>, 2007. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780195308808" class="internal">ISBN 978-0195308808</a></li>
<li><i>Western Muslims and the future of Islam</i>, 2004. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/019517111X" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-517111-X</a></li>
<li><i>Islam, the West, and the Challenge of Modernity</i>, 2001. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0860373118" class="internal">ISBN 0-86037-311-8</a></li>
