<p><a name="About_Tariq_Ramadan" id="About_Tariq_Ramadan"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Tariq_Ramadan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: About Tariq Ramadan">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">About Tariq Ramadan</span></h3>
